Class InfectedState

  • java.lang.Object
    • sample.InfectedState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HealthState

    public class InfectedState
extends java.lang.Object
implements HealthState
    Concrete Healt State This is our infected state When every time a individual in this state moves its reduces its lifetime. When life time reaches the zero it will go Dead State It also counts backwards from 25 to go hospital. When count reaches the zero simulator can take this individual to a hospital if there is a empty room
